      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:54:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克敦促泰晤士水务公司清理自身的财务混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/sunak-presses-thames-water-to-clean-up-its-own-financial-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克政府正在敦促泰晤士水务公司及其陷入困境的母公司单独解决其财务困难，这增加了英国最大水务公司面临的危机将在未来几周内加深的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/sunak-presses-thames-water-to-clean-up-its-own-financial-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙反对党社会主义者可能支持一些政府措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/portugal-s-opposition-socialists-may-back-some-government-measures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙社会党表示，可能会在议会支持该国新的少数派中右翼政府的一些措施，同时投票反对其不同意的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/portugal-s-opposition-socialists-may-back-some-government-measures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:06:44 GMT</pubDate>
